01:05:38.848 --> 01:05:40.016
&lrm;Anh biết.

896
01:05:41.392 --> 01:05:42.393
&lrm;Anh sẽ tìm ra nó.

897
01:05:43.686 --> 01:05:44.937
&lrm;Ruby!

898
01:05:47.148 --> 01:05:48.566
&lrm;Ruby!

899
