01:07:09.647 --> 01:07:12.274
&lrm;Hiệu Ball Park Frank đến từ Fenway đây.

922
01:07:12.775 --> 01:07:14.068
&lrm;Fenway.

923
01:07:14.151 --> 01:07:15.569
&lrm;Ruby!

924
01:07:15.653 --> 01:07:17.071
&lrm;Ruby.

